data.description: Exceptional opportunity to rehab a valuable historical home in the Village of Hinsdale.  Or there's the opportunity to focus on new construction in a highly desirable location of DuPage County. The lot size offers 90 ft. frontage on South County Line Road. It is 192 ft. deep creating a .40 acre parcel with mature trees. Build your dream home! Award winning schools-Oak Elementary, Hinsdale Middle School, and Hinsdale Central High School! Great proximity to shopping, expressways and Metra station. Do not disturb the owner or walk the lot without a confirmed appointment with a broker. Plat of Survey and Pre-planning Review provided.
